original_title: Queens: Old Bowery Bay Road - 29th Street
text:
Old Bowery Bay Road, south side, between 29th and 31st Streets, showing a rear view of the John Alsop farmhouse, viewed from 21st Ave. Some of the owners of this house were John Alsop 1852 and C. Debevoise 1860-1873. This house was demolished in March or May of 1925. No. 20-54 31st Street, a four story apartment house now occupies the site. This is a set of three views.

May 1923.

Eugene L. Ambruster Collection.
